ModelAdmin for django-mptt based tree. (Based on FEINCMS tree editor,
see http://www.feinheit.ch/, https://github.com/matthiask/feincms)

Usage:
-----
 *  Install "django-sakkada"
 *  Import "sakkada.admin.mptt_tree.MpttTreeAdmin"
 *  Set "MpttTreeAdmin" as class of admin model
 *  Set extended template name in "mptt_tree_parent_template" property if required
 *  Copy static "admin/*" to your project static folder
    or add "sakkada.admin.mptt_tree" to your INSTALLED_APPS.
 *  Copy templates "admin/mptt_tree/*" to your project/application template folder
    or add "sakkada.admin.mptt_tree" to your INSTALLED_APPS.

Example usage:
-------------
from django.contrib import admin
from sakkada.admin.mptt_tree import MpttTreeAdmin


class SomeTreeAdmin(MpttTreeAdmin, admin.ModelAdmin):
    mptt_tree_parent_template = 'admin/mptt_tree_parent_template.html'

admin.site.register(Some, SomeTreeAdmin)
